sentences: Holly Suzette Dunn (August 22, 1957 – November 14, 2016) was an American country music singer and songwriter.
Dunn recorded for MTM Records between 1985 and 1988, Warner Bros. Records between 1988 and 1993, and River North Records between 1995 and 1997.
